<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta name="description" content="Blockchain Education DAO for enhancing global education through decentralized technologies.">
    <title>Blockchain Education DAO</title>
    <style>
        /* General Styling */
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f4f4f9;
        }

        header {
            background-color: #333;
            color: white;
            padding: 10px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }

        header nav ul {
            list-style-type: none;
            padding: 0;
        }

        header nav ul li {
            display: inline;
            margin: 0 15px;
        }

        header nav ul li a {
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        header nav ul li a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        section {
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px;
            background-color: white;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }

        h1, h2 {
            color: #333;
        }

        footer {
            background-color: #333;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px;
            position: fixed;
            width: 100%;
            bottom: 0;
        }

        /* Form Styling */
        .form-container {
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        input[type="text"], input[type="email"] {
            padding: 10px;
            width: 80%;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            border: 1px solid #ccc;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }

        button {
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: #4CAF50;
            color: white;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 4px;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        button:hover {
            background-color: #45a049;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <!-- Navbar -->
    <header>
        <nav>
            <ul>
                <li><a href="#home">Home</a></li>
                <li><a href="#about">About</a></li>
                <li><a href="#community">Community</a></li>
                <li><a href="#airdrop">Airdrop</a></li>
                <li><a href="#contact">Contact</a></li>
            </ul>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <!-- Home Section -->
    <section id="home">
        <h1>Welcome to Blockchain Education DAO</h1>
        <p>The Blockchain Education DAO is dedicated to revolutionizing global education by leveraging decentralized technologies. Our mission is to create a decentralized platform for learning, where educational content is verified, accessible, and rewarded using blockchain technology.</p>
    </section>

    <!-- About Section -->
    <section id="about">
        <h2>About Blockchain Education DAO</h2>
        <p>This DAO (Decentralized Autonomous Organization) is built to support educational content creators, students, and educators by utilizing the power of blockchain technology. Through decentralization, we aim to democratize education, allowing anyone, anywhere, to access, share, and earn from educational content.</p>
    </section>

    <!-- Community Section -->
    <section id="community">
        <h2>Join the Community</h2>
        <p>Our community is focused on spreading the knowledge and benefits of blockchain education. Join us as we grow this revolutionary movement. Engage in discussions, share resources, and participate in events that advance the future of education.</p>
    </section>

    <!-- Airdrop Section -->
    <section id="airdrop">
        <h2>Claim Your Airdrop</h2>
        <p>As part of our mission to expand our community, we are giving away free tokens to new users who participate in our airdrop campaign. Sign up below to claim your tokens and get involved in the Blockchain Education DAO!</p>

        <!-- Airdrop Form -->
        <div class="form-container">
            <form id="airdrop-form">
                <input type="text" id="full-name" placeholder="Enter your full name" required><br>
                <input type="email" id="email" placeholder="Enter your email address" required><br>
                <button type="submit">Claim Airdrop</button>
            </form>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Contact Section -->
    <section id="contact">
        <h2>Contact Us</h2>
        <p>If you have any questions or would like to collaborate, reach out to us at <strong>contact@blockeducationdao.com</strong>.</p>
    </section>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2024 Blockchain Education DAO | Follow us on <a href="https://twitter.com/MerionaVibes" target="_blank">Twitter @MerionaVibes</a></p>
    </footer>

    <script>
        // Handle airdrop form submission
        document.getElementById("airdrop-form").addEventListener("submit", function(event) {
            event.preventDefault();

            // Collect form data
            const name = document.getElementById("full-name").value;
            const email = document.getElementById("email").value;

            // Display a success message
            alert("Thank you for signing up, " + name + "! Your airdrop request has been received.");

            // Clear the form
            document.getElementById("airdrop-form").reset();
        });
    </script>
</body>
</html>
